    <!-- Chosen Palette: Earthy Calm (Warm neutrals like beige/off-white, soft brown text, muted green accent) -->
    <!-- Application Structure Plan: The SPA is designed as an interactive dashboard. The core interaction is a tab-like navigation system with buttons for each day of the week, plus a special button for "Pasto Libero" guidance. This structure makes accessing daily meal plans immediate and intuitive. Key reference information, like general guidelines, is placed in a collapsible section at the top to keep the main view uncluttered but the info readily accessible. A summary visualization (a macronutrient donut chart) is included at the bottom to provide a high-level, educational overview of the diet's principles. This design transforms a static text document into a user-friendly, task-oriented tool. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
    - Report Info: Full 7-day meal plan. Goal: Organize & Inform. Method: Interactive daily schedule. Interaction: User clicks a day button to display that day's meals in formatted cards with icons. Justification: Most direct and user-friendly way to navigate a weekly schedule.
    - Report Info: "Linee Guida" & "Consigli Aggiuntivi". Goal: Inform. Method: Collapsible text block. Interaction: Click to expand/collapse. Justification: Keeps important but non-daily information accessible without taking up screen space.
    - Report Info: Macronutrient balance concept. Goal: Visualize diet composition. Method: Donut Chart (Chart.js/Canvas) showing ideal macro split. Interaction: Static weekly summary view with tooltips. Justification: Provides a high-level data insight into the diet's macronutrient balance, promoting understanding of dietary principles. Added text provides context on micros, water, and Kcal.
    - Report Info: Meal types (colazione, pranzo, etc.). Goal: Inform & structure. Method: Styled cards with headers and icons. Interaction: Static display within the daily view. Justification: Clearly delineates meals for easy readability.
    - Report Info: "Pasto Libero" guidelines. Goal: Inform & support. Method: Dedicated static content section. Interaction: User clicks a "Pasto Libero" button to display the guidelines. Justification: Provides important lifestyle advice, including tips for meals surrounding the "sgarro", separate from daily meal plans. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
